<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">It gave a very concise view of the Amish that I found very interesting and was an integral part of the story. It wasn&apos;t in the least bit offensive or <a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">It gave a very concise view of the Amish that I found very interesting and was an integral part of the story. It wasn't in the least bit offensive or "preachy" -- simply an insight into the Amish community and their beliefs. I found it fascinating. <a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
